data.description:
Location! Location! Location! Very close to Dahlgren Naval Base and Harry Nice Bridge! Freshly Painted throughout, LVP flooring on main level... Lovely 4 Bedroom 2.5 bath Colonial on almost an acre lot. Main level is open & bright with a gas fireplace in great room. Separate Dining Room, an office, play room or exercise room. Kitchen with breakfast nook that leads to 12 x 12 deck and view of large level back yard that backs to woods! Home has "Smart" features such as a thermostat, door ring etc. Shed in back yard to store your garden tools and a Fire pit for family and friend gatherings. Call and set up a private showing! Pets accepted on a case by case basis, pet fee required (2 pet minimum) A MINIMUM CREDIT SCORE OF 600, MONTHLY INCOME REQUIREMENT IS $8,100 (3 TIMES THE MONTHLY RENT) THERE IS A PROCESSING FEE OF $50 PER ADULT APPLICANT

Tenant pays for all utilities, NO SMOKING INSIDE HOME!
